{"tid":2513041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全港外傭須強檢、疑強制打針　工會：我們並非帶病毒者","createTime":"2021-05-02T08:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T08:14:08.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"01ef3bc1da82d7ff47bb09af6bad8a6ecbf770d0","tid":2513041,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:08:53.000Z","msg":"全港外傭須強檢、疑強制打針　工會：我們並非帶病毒者<br />\n<br />\n因應有外傭確診變種病毒，全港 37 萬名外傭須在本月 9 日或之前做檢測。有外傭團體不滿意政府新措施，二人一組舉牌抗議，直言強檢及要打針的政策，是歧視及不必要。<br />\n<br />\n亞洲移居人士聯盟( Asian Migrants&rsquo; Coordination Body ) 下午在中環遮打道舉牌抗議。參與的外傭二人一組，有人手寫口號牌靜默站立。牌上寫上「我們並非帶病毒者 ( We are not virus carrier)」等字句。其中一個主辦者，在港工作 26 年的 Dolores 指，抗議行動是想向政府的新措施表達憤怒。她指在未有強檢令前，組織一直鼓勵成員做檢測，但反對政府將檢測及打疫苗變成強性質，擔心做法令社會歧視外傭。"},{"pid":"55e33f3db461e4ccb80d7ba6a98f0ed9c19aa949","tid":2513041,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:09:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/335AwIm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F335AwIm&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=755d7a0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/335AwIm</a>"},{"pid":"dc47b5d5e35ce4e81f99e3b572008a64320e0356","tid":2513041,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:09:50.000Z","msg":"罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8c778104ac9fdcbcc531e867f9530fbd388cd2","tid":2513041,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:10:24.000Z","msg":"國際社會知道會唔會嘈呢"},{"pid":"0ebba5fcbcb53259165ac6dd5ff8ab132bb47831","tid":2513041,"uid":264974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f8c778104ac9fdcbcc531e867f9530fbd388cd2","tid":2513041,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:10:24.000Z","msg":"國際社會知道會唔會嘈呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"外國左派會覺得好正！疫苗呀😍正呀！"}]}